title: Julio Trecenti
text:
Hi! My name is Julio Trecenti (aka Data Janitor)
I’m a Statistician and have PhD at IME-USP, Brazil

Experience
I do a lot of things!

Tech Director at ABJ
Partner at Terranova Consulting
Teacher at Curso-R
Assistant professor at Insper
Post doctorate researcher at Unifesp



Main interests

Jurimetrics, Web Scraping and Neural Networks
R enthusiast, but I use Python if needed
Open Data activist



Personal

I like dogs, piano, and text in bullet points
I write mostly in Portuguese. Stay tuned for content in English!
I love my wife, family and friends
